      <title>拉马福萨（Ramaphosa）与其他领导人一起猛击特朗普的加沙计划以色列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/ramaphosa-joins-other-leaders-to-slam-israel-trump-s-gaza-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三个发展中国家的领导人谴责以色列在加沙对哈马斯的战争处决，并表示美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）提议吞并该领土，并将其所有公民驱逐出境将是违法的，并且属于“种族清洗”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/ramaphosa-joins-other-leaders-to-slam-israel-trump-s-gaza-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:47:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在非洲第一个G-20总统职位上，武器挥霍了霸道援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/arms-splurge-overshadows-aid-at-africa-s-first-g-20-presidency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲在20个国家的东道国集团的第一个转弯被认为是发展的巨大努力，但目睹了富裕的经济体进一步向武器求助于援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/arms-splurge-overshadows-aid-at-africa-s-first-g-20-presidency</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:45:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟考虑为潜在的乌克兰谈话命名特使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/eu-to-consider-naming-special-envoy-for-potential-ukraine-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟的领导人将在下周的一次会议上讨论一个特使的任命，该特使代表该集团，以结束俄罗斯入侵乌克兰的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/eu-to-consider-naming-special-envoy-for-potential-ukraine-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:36:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚的石油公司将前石油工人联盟主任为能源部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/petro-names-former-head-of-oil-workers-union-as-energy-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚的古斯塔沃·佩特罗（Gustavo Petro）有望将埃德温·帕尔玛（Edwin Palma）命名为他内阁内部动荡不安的新能源部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/petro-names-former-head-of-oil-workers-union-as-energy-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 14:55:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯坦福德冻结招聘，因为学校面临特朗普的资金威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/stanford-freezes-hiring-as-colleges-face-trump-funding-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯坦福大学（Stanford University）正在实施招聘冻结，因为美国各地的大学与特朗普政府削减了严重资金的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/stanford-freezes-hiring-as-colleges-face-trump-funding-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 14:52:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>G-20财务负责人由于气候融资变成粘性而无法达到共同点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/g-20-finance-chiefs-support-south-africa-s-call-for-solidarity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长聚集在开普敦，参加了20个富裕经济体团体的会议，未能就气候融资等一系列问题达成共识。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/g-20-finance-chiefs-support-south-africa-s-call-for-solidarity</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 14:24:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛（Goldman Sachs</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/goldman-sachs-removes-diversity-targets-after-trump-dei-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团公司（Goldman Sachs Group Inc.）从关键的监管申请中删除了多样性目标，成为最新的华尔街公司，在唐纳德·特朗普总统的行政命令之后，脱离了更具代表性劳动力的特定目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/goldman-sachs-removes-diversity-targets-after-trump-dei-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 14:07:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，加拿大，墨西哥的关税要生效，并补充说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/trump-says-canada-mexico-tariffs-to-take-effect-new-china-duty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，加拿大和墨西哥的25％关税正计划于3月4日登机，并表示他将对中国进口税征收10％的税，这将加深他与美国最大的贸易伙伴的战斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/trump-says-canada-mexico-tariffs-to-take-effect-new-china-duty</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 14:01:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普政府取消了FDA疫苗顾问的会议，冒着流感延迟的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/trump-administration-cancels-meeting-of-fda-vaccine-advisers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府取消了即将举行的食品药品监督管理局疫苗咨询委员会的会议，此举可能会使在即将到来的季节及时产生流感射击的努力变得复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/trump-administration-cancels-meeting-of-fda-vaccine-advisers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 03:41:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
